{"version": 2, "width": 110, "height": 32, "timestamp": 1779238650, "idle_time_limit": 3.0, "env": {"SHELL": "/usr/bin/zsh", "TERM": null}, "title": "Karmada Agent Skills POC — demo.sh walkthrough"}
[0.010541, "o", "\u001b[2J\u001b[H\u001b[1;36mKarmada Agent Skills — POC walkthrough\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2mProof of concept for LFX 2026 T2 mentorship 'Build Karmada Agent Skills'\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2mUpstream: karmada-io/community#190\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;33m$ bash hack/agent-skills/demo.sh\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.022997, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m=== 1. Regenerate auto schema docs from upstream CRDs ===\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.768533, "o", "wrote 68 field rows → knowledge/10-propagation-schema.md\r\n"]
[3.892142, "o", "wrote 62 field rows → knowledge/11-override-schema.md\r\n"]
[3.900583, "o", "  (re-generated 10-propagation-schema.md and 11-override-schema.md)\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m=== 2. Generate the multi-country policy from intent JSON ===\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.57965, "o", "  wrote /tmp/generated-policy.yaml\r\n"]
[5.582097, "o", "    apiVersion: policy.karmada.io/v1alpha1\r\n    kind: PropagationPolicy\r\n    metadata:\r\n      name: global-frontend\r\n      namespace: default\r\n    spec:\r\n      resourceSelectors:\r\n      - apiVersion: apps/v1\r\n        kind: Deployment\r\n        name: global-frontend\r\n      - apiVersion: v1\r\n        kind: Service\r\n        name: global-frontend\r\n      placement:\r\n        clusterAffinities:\r\n        - affinityName: apac-primary\r\n          clusterNames:\r\n          - sg-prod-1\r\n          - sg-prod-2\r\n        - affinityName: apac-backup\r\n          clusterNames:\r\n          - id-prod-1\r\n        - affinityName: europe-primary\r\n          clusterNames:\r\n          - de-prod-1\r\n"]
[5.582445, "o", "    ...\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m=== 3. Audit the generated policy (should be clean) ===\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[7.25326, "o", "ok — no findings\r\n"]
[7.260802, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m=== 4. Audit a deliberately broken policy (should report R5 = JSONPath misuse) ===\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[8.934967, "o", "[ERROR] R5     docs[0].spec.overrideRules[0].overriders.plaintext[0].path: path '$.spec.template.spec.containers[0].image' is JSONPath; OverridePolicy requires JSON Pointer (RFC 6901, starts with '/')\r\n"]
[8.943039, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m=== 5. Audit a misplaced-replicaScheduling policy (should report R1) ===\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[10.624822, "o", "[ERROR] R1     docs[0].spec.replicaScheduling: replicaScheduling is misplaced; move it under spec.placement.replicaScheduling\r\n"]
[10.633584, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m=== 6. Debug a propagation failure (should report verdict=schedule-failed) ===\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.306559, "o", "{\r\n  \"verdict\": \"schedule-failed\",\r\n  \"hop_reached\": \"ResourceBinding\",\r\n  \"evidence\": [\r\n    \"found target object Service/checkout\",\r\n    \"1 policy(ies) match: checkout-pp\",\r\n    \"1 binding(s) present\",\r\n    \"RB.status[Scheduled]=False reason='NoClusterFit' message='no cluster matches affinity environment=production'\"\r\n  ],\r\n  \"next_steps\": [\r\n    \"confirm Cluster objects have the labels the placement expects\",\r\n    \"if clusterAffinities (plural), the first group with any match short-circuits \\u2014 list preferred groups first\",\r\n    \"see knowledge/02-troubleshooting.md case T-NoSchedule\"\r\n  ]\r\n}\r\n"]
[13.917124, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m=== 7. Run the test suite ===\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[16.598288, "o", "..............\r\n----------------------------------------------------------------------\r\nRan 14 tests in 0.964s\r\n\r\nOK\r\n"]
[18.201611, "o", "\u001b[1mDone. All seven steps demonstrate one of the POC's deterministic helpers.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[18.202145, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36mWhat you just saw:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  • schema docs auto-extracted from real Karmada CRDs\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  • a multi-country policy generated from a JSON intent\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[18.202218, "o", "\u001b[2m  • the auditor catching the two most common LLM mistakes (R1, R5)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  • a propagation failure diagnosed from a captured snapshot\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[18.202235, "o", "\u001b[2m  • 14 unit tests, all green\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
